Customize search, provide relevant results, and ensure security in Search Manager. Improve search with Search Manager and Search Analytics, and see more results with advanced lookup search.

IdeaExchange Delivered: Improve Search for Users with Search Manager (Generally Available)
Improve search efficiency and relevance by customizing search for your users in Search Manager. Create configurations for search channels, filter search for your users with rules, and configure objects to always search.
Provide Relevant Results with Objects to Always Search in Search Manager (Generally Available)
Select objects to always search in a global search configuration. Tailor your selection for a specific user profile.
Ensure Security in Search with Search Manager
Apply field-level security to custom fields that contain sensitive information in Search Manager.
Improve Search with Insights from Search Analytics (Pilot)
Analyze search-related data with the built-in dashboard or build your own dashboard. Use insights to make search engine changes, optimize content, and train users.
title: Improving Search Efficiency with Salesforce Search Manager
